1
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:03,480
Are you thirsty?

2
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:05,040
Does anything else hurt?

3
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:06,520
Any scrapes or bruises?

4
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:14,880
What's wrong?

5
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:20,560
You're right.

6
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:24,000
If I had just warmed up properly,

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:26,280
I wouldn't have been such a burden to everyone.

8
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,800
With your big brother here,

9
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,320
everything is taken care of, right?

10
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:36,160
Are you mad at me?

11
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:38,240
Why would I be?

12
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,280
You're clearly a little upset...

13
00:00:45,720 --> 00:00:47,840
But it's nice, isn't it?

14
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:49,840
Running with everyone again after all this time.

15
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:52,080
Even if...

16
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:53,920
the results were pretty pathetic.

17
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:59,320
You didn't compete to meet everyone's expectations.

18
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:03,160
You did it because you followed your heart.

19
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,920
My... heart?

20
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,640
I suppose so.

21
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,360
Well,

22
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,240
I'm heading back to class.

23
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,360
Thanks.

24
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,600
Big brother.

25
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,640
Iijima Hinata...

26
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,200
You finally called me brother.

27
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,760
Shut up...

28
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,320
Just get out of here.

29
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,000
As for me...
